    <title>Power Agent MCP - Enterprise AI SDK for Microsoft Power Platform</title>
    <authors>DarBot Labs</authors>
    <owners>DarBot Labs</owners>
    <description>
      Enterprise-grade Model Context Protocol (MCP) server providing AI assistants with comprehensive programmatic access to the Microsoft Power Platform ecosystem. Features 254+ specialized tools spanning Power Platform CLI operations, native Dataverse management, SQL Server integration, and Copilot Studio adaptive cards for complete AI-driven enterprise automation.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>
      Initial release featuring:
      - 254 specialized tools for complete Power Platform coverage
      - Native Dataverse integration with 25 dedicated operations
      - SQL Server integration with 7 database management tools
      - Adaptive Cards SDK with 10 Copilot Studio tools
      - Enterprise authentication (Service Principal, Managed Identity)
      - Production-ready error handling and monitoring
      - Comprehensive API documentation and examples
    </releaseNotes>
    <summary>Enterprise AI SDK enabling natural language automation across Microsoft Power Platform, Dataverse, SQL Server, and Copilot Studio through 254+ specialized MCP tools.</summary>    <language>en-US</language>
